Privacy Notice
==============

This privacy notice discloses the privacy practices for the website
tracker.craptobuy.com and its browser extension. Change history for this
privacy notice can be viewed at:
https://github.com/crccheck/CrapCrapCrap/blob/master/PRIVACY

Browser extension
-----------------

The browser extension records no personal information.

Information Collection, Use, and Sharing
----------------------------------------

We are the sole owners of the information collected on this site. We only have
access to/collect information that you voluntarily give us via email or other
direct contact from you. We will not sell or rent this information to anyone.

We will use your information to respond to you, regarding the reason you
contacted us. We will not share your information with any third party outside
of our organization, other than as necessary to fulfill your request.

We may email you when:
* this privacy policy changes
* you subscribe to an alert

Your Access to and Control Over Information
-------------------------------------------

* You can view all information we have on your account pages.
* You can permanently delete all information associated with account by deleting your account.
* You can export all your information (TODO)
